<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#006d98">س ٩:</span> مَا أَرْكَانُ شَهَادَةِ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللهُ؟ وَمَا الدَّلِيلُ؟<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>شَهَادَةُ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللهُ،<span style="color:#006d98"> لَهَا رُكْنَانِ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">الْأَوَّلُ:</span> النَّفْيُ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَهُوَ قَوْلُ:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(لَا إِلَهَ)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">الثَّانِي:</span> الْإِثْبَاتُ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَهُوَ قَوْلُ:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(إِلَّا اللهُ)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#006d98">والدَّلِيلُ قَوْلُ اللهِ تَعَالَى:</span> <span style="color:#947721">{فَمَنْ يَكْفُرْ بِالطَّاغُوتِ وَيُؤْمِنْ بِاللَّهِ فَقَدِ اسْتَمْسَكَ بِالْعُرْوَةِ الْوُثْقَى}</span> <span style="color:#008000">(١)</span> <span style="color:#707070">[البقرة: ٢٥٦]</span>،<span style="color:#006d98"> فَقَوْلُهُ:</span> <span style="color:#947721">{فَمَنْ يَكْفُرْ بِالطَّاغُوتِ}</span> هَذَا دَلِيلُ النَّفْيِ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَقَوْلُهُ:</span> <span style="color:#947721">{وَيُؤْمِنْ بِاللَّهِ}</span> هَذَا دَلِيلُ الْإِثْبَاتِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>* * *<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#006d98">س ١٠:</span> مَا شُرُوطُ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللهُ؟<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>شُرُوطُ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللهُ ثَمَانِيَةٌ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَهِيَ:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>١ - الْعِلْمُ الْمُنَافِي لِلْجَهْلِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٢ - الْيَقِينُ الْمُنَافِي للشَّكِّ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٣ - الْإِخْلَاصُ الْمُنَافِي لِلشِّرْكِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>٤ - الصِّدْقُ المُنَافِي لِلْكَذِبِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٥ - الْمَحَبَّةُ الْمُنَافِيَةُ لِلْبُغْضِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) قَالَ سَعِيدُ بْنُ جُبَيْرٍ -رحمه الله-: «الْعُروَةُ الوُثقَى: لَا إِلَهَ إلَّا اللهُ». [«تَفسِير الطَّبَرِي» (٤/ ٥٦٠)].</p> </div>